reviewText:
I was so excited when I got this video,until I watched it. You rarely see the Olsentwins, it's more a fashion show of their clothes,but not worn by themselves, no by amateur child models.
I sold it the next day,to an other Olsenfan,I was so dissapointed. If you wan't something cool buy:
Hawaiin Beach Party, Winning London or Our lips are sealed, or one of their older movies.
Don't buy it,if you wanna see a lot of the olsentwins.

WHY WOULD SOME ONE NOT LIKE LOOKING AT TWO VERY BEAUTIFUL GIRLS FOR THE WHOLE MOVIE. I SHURE ENJOYED THIS MOVIE.
MY ADVISE TO YOU:
DRINK DR. PEPPER

I've been an Olsen Fan ever since Full House and this is the first time they've had a video out that I didn't want. It really is a waste of money. It would be nice to see the Fashion Show (which was temporarily shown on their website), I don't see any reason to buy the video only to watch it a handful of times and then never see it again. Unless your daughter (or son) is seriously planning on becoming a fashion designer and wants the video to maybe learn a little more about fashion  don't bother buying it. Maybe borrow it from a friend or the library or something instead.

Here you will see the making of Mary-Kate and Ashleys FASHION LINE. Can you believe they went this far? I can't wait to see what they will be doing next! They show you their sports wear clothing, swimming, and their pajamas. Soon they will be going into bathrooms and bedrooms. The video is all about the fashion line that will be hitting every Wal-Mart store so keep your eyes open and you might just find yourself looking at Mary-Kate and Ashleys newer fashion line. Check it out!
it's sooooooo cool i like it mka rock's you've got to have it It goes behind-the-scenes of the marykateandashley Wal-Mart fashion line.  I recommend all Olsen fans alike to buy Fashion Forward!
It's awsome i'm 15 & have grown up w/ the twins me & my twin sis love it! Its cool for teens & tweens!

This video is really cool.  It goes behind-the-scenes of the marykateandashley Wal-Mart fashion line.  Rockers, Gotti 13, rock the house while young female models strut their stuff wearing the newest Olsen fashions.  The Olsens' WINNING LONDON male co-stars host this awesome fashion show.  Also, Mary-Kate and Ashley themselves talk about their line.  I recommend all Olsen fans alike to buy Fashion Forward!
